{"tid":1011651,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]懷疑個肚生蟲","createTime":"2019-02-07T03:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T15:59:03.000Z","uid":5891,"like":183,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfeb577b59d68b143981525de46a658987fb5b2","tid":1011651,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"屌，頭先大解完果陣，見到啲糞便有啲白白地色嘅條狀物<br />\n我果下冇特別在意，去拎廁紙抆，仲心諗唔通尋晚食炒麵搞到屙啲咁嘅嘢<br />\n但係諗諗下，尋晚食完嘅嘢，正常應該消化咗先係，點會喺呢到屙出嚟<br />\n果時先意識到應該係個肚生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係啲廁紙已經遮住左啲條狀物，冇得仔細觀察係咩嚟<br />\n不過上網搵過啲圖，應該似係絛蟲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣就去買藥食&hellip;&hellip;新年流流搞啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4c1f35e6d564898117c553eb6e74890f5a769c","tid":1011651,"uid":1354,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:15:35.000Z","msg":"精蟲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d58f2c28ee834d22a087912c82a68ca779b4ab","tid":1011651,"uid":104618,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"捉返條蟲帶去睇醫生"},{"pid":"1c450d7470204b0e1a6a82d8c69903eac8dbc2b9","tid":1011651,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"成日食生嘢?"},{"pid":"899fa34675bd4c65e9d5e8e836f6ea6b8b6a396b","tid":1011651,"uid":206337,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f09fe793af05711360301933d43438e35ddad4","tid":1011651,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:19:56.000Z","msg":"飲西梅汁，痾晒佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d121a0f82cfb4bae75b923a7046eafcdc0106a5d","tid":1011651,"uid":128600,"like":45,"dis